{"id": "1440765286063276053", "channel_id": "1440765286063276053", "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "content": "This is a piece of feedback for... Way way later in the development cycle now, because of how much game design/development power it would require.\n\nBut one of the things that kept me playing even when story had me stuck was events. I was lucky to fall right into fun ones at the start, like Lily's event with it's special orison mechanic and Sorells event. Even the Elsworth expedition one with the expeditioners.\n\nEach event having a skill tree, and quite a substantial mechanic that you could build/mess around with. I somewhat miss that with arc2 events tending to be a single gimmick relic and a single fight.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T18:06:52.322000+00:00", "thread_id": "1440765286063276053", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-19T18:07:44.547000+00:00"}
